divs: Sighting DetailsStanding outside in the early morning Florida hours around 6:15am taking pictures of Venus & Jupiter, a very clear, big bright orb appeared in only one of the pictures. I took several pictures before and after and this is only picture with the orb. I did not see the orb when taking the picture.
Summary: Orb in picture with Venus & Jupiter in Florida morning sky
